\id 2TH  
\h 2 Aj Tesalónica 
\toc3 2Tes. 
\toc2 2 Aj Tesalónica 
\toc1 Tkabꞌ Tuꞌj Pabl kye Nimil aj Tesalónica 
\mt1 Tkabꞌ Tuꞌj Pabl kye Nimil aj Tesalónica 
\ip A tkabꞌ uꞌj kye nimil toj tnam Tesalónica junx taꞌ tnabꞌljo xnaqꞌtzbꞌil tukꞌa tnejil tuꞌj Pabl kye nimil antza. Me tojjo tkabꞌ uꞌj, nimx nyolin tiꞌjjo aj tul meltzꞌaj qAjaw. Tbꞌajlinxi ttzꞌibꞌin Pabljo tnejil uꞌj, bꞌeꞌx ul tqanil te, qa aye nimil antza nimx yajbꞌil otaq tzaj kyiꞌj, ex otaq chi bꞌisin, quꞌn kubꞌ kyximin qa a tkabꞌ tulil qAjaw Jesucrist otaq bꞌaj toj kywutz. Tuꞌntziꞌn luꞌn, xi ttzꞌibꞌin Pabljo tkabꞌ tuꞌj kye, tuꞌntzin tqe kykꞌuꞌj, ex tuꞌn tchewx kyanmin tojjo jniꞌ yajbꞌil n-ikyꞌxtaq kyuꞌn, ex tuꞌn tqe kykꞌuꞌj qa naꞌmtaq tul Jesucrist tkabꞌ majin. 
\ip Tuꞌn ttzyetjo uꞌj lo, xi tqꞌoꞌn Pabl chjonte te Dios, quꞌn ajo kynimbꞌil ex kykꞌuꞌjbꞌil nimil toj Tesalónica kyjataq tchꞌiy. Te tibꞌajxi, xi tchikyꞌbꞌin kye qa ajo Tkawbꞌil Dios ilxixtaq tiꞌj tuꞌn tjapin, ex ajo tkabꞌ tulil qAjaw, twutzxix, me naꞌmxtaq tkanin tqꞌijil. Ex atzin il twutz txꞌotxꞌ, a tzeꞌnku n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn, ilxixtaq tiꞌj tuꞌn tjapin. Me okxixpe kxeꞌl tetz toj il, ajxix tjapin tqꞌijiljo ichin, a ntqꞌma Pabl, a aj ilxixch (\xt 2:3\xt*). 
\ip Kyxoljo yol te qꞌol nabꞌl tiꞌj kychwinqil nimil, ajo ntzaj tqꞌoꞌn toj tbꞌajsbꞌil tuꞌj, ntzaj tqꞌoꞌn juntl yol te nukꞌbꞌil tiꞌjjo tuꞌn kyaqꞌnin tuꞌn kykanbꞌinte kywaꞌ toj tumilxix, a tzeꞌnkuxjo yekꞌbꞌil kyij tqꞌoꞌn Pabl kye, teꞌ tten kyukꞌa. 
\c 1  
\s1 Jun qꞌolbꞌil 
\p  
\v 1 Ayiꞌn Pabl nxi ntzꞌibꞌinjiꞌy uꞌj luꞌn, junx tukꞌa Silvano ex Timotey. Nxi ntzꞌibꞌiꞌn kyeꞌy, ayiꞌy Ttanim Dios toj tnam Tesalónica,\x + \xo 1:1\xt Kybꞌi. 17:1; 1Tes. 1:1.\x* a ayiꞌy ma tzꞌok kymujbꞌin kyibꞌa tukꞌa qMan Dios ex tukꞌa qAjaw Jesucrist.  
\v 2 Chjonte qMan Dios tuꞌn t-xtalbꞌil ex tnukꞌbꞌil kyibꞌaja, a qTata ex qAjaw Jesucrist. 
\s1 A Dios kkawil kyibꞌaj aj il, aj tul qAjaw Jesús 
\p  
\v 3 Erman, kukx nxi qqꞌonjiꞌy chjonte te qMan Dios kyiꞌja. Ex il tiꞌjjo lo tuꞌn tkubꞌ qbꞌinchiꞌn, quꞌn a kynimbꞌila nchꞌiyxix wen, junx tukꞌa kykꞌuꞌjbꞌila teyile junjun.  
\v 4 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, kukx nqo yoliꞌn kyiꞌja kyxol kykyaqil Ttanim Dios, quꞌn tuꞌn nimxix kynimbꞌila ex tuꞌn waꞌlqexixa toj tkyaqiljo nya bꞌaꞌn ntzaj kyuꞌnxjal, ex toj tkyaqiljo bꞌis n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn. 
\p  
\v 5 Ate luꞌn nyekꞌinte qa tzꞌaqlexix Dios tukꞌa tkawbꞌil, quꞌn toj tkyaqiljo jniꞌ n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn, ma tzaj tqꞌoꞌn Dios kyokixa toj kyaꞌj.  
\v 6 Quꞌn tzꞌaqlexix te Dios. Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, il tiꞌj tuꞌn ttzaj tqꞌoj Dios kyiꞌjjo ayeꞌ nchi yajin kyiꞌja.  
\v 7 Ex ktzajil tqꞌoꞌn ajlabꞌl kyeꞌy, ayiꞌy n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn; ikyxjo tzeꞌnku qeꞌ ktzajil tqꞌoꞌn ajlabꞌl qeꞌy, toj tqꞌijil, aj tul qAjaw Jesús toj kyaꞌj tukꞌa qꞌaqꞌ njulin wen, ex kyukꞌa jniꞌ t-angel.  
\v 8 Ex tzul qꞌolte tkawbꞌil kujxix kyibꞌaj kykyaqiljo, a mi ẍi nimin tiꞌj Dios, ex mi xkubꞌ kynimin a Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil te qAjaw Jesucrist.  
\v 9 Ex ktzajil qꞌoꞌn kawbꞌil kujxix te jun majx, ex kchi elix lajet najchaq tkꞌatz Dios toj kyaꞌj, jaꞌ nqoptzꞌaje qAjaw tukꞌa tkyaqil tipin.  
\v 10 Tkyaqiljo lo kbꞌajil, aj tul tqꞌijil, tuꞌn tul qAjaw, tuꞌn tjaw nimsin tbꞌi, ex tuꞌn kyjaw kaꞌylaj tkyaqil nimil, junx kyukꞌiy, ayiꞌy ma txi kyniminjiꞌy a yol xi qqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy. 
\p  
\v 11 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, kukx nqo naꞌnjiꞌy Dios kyiꞌja, tuꞌn kybꞌeta toj tumilxix, a tzeꞌnkuxjo kyokliꞌn, teꞌ ẍi tzaj txkoꞌn tuꞌn. Ex nqo kubꞌsin qwutza te Dios, tuꞌn kytzaj oniꞌn tuꞌn, tuꞌn tjapin bꞌajjo jniꞌ kyajbꞌila bꞌaꞌn ex tkyaqil kyaqꞌiꞌn, a nkybꞌinchiꞌn tuꞌn kynimbꞌila, noq tukꞌa tkyaqil tipin qMan.  
\v 12 Ikytziꞌn, kjawil nimsit tbꞌi qAjaw Jesucrist toj kychwinqila, ex ikyxjo kyeꞌ ex kchi jawil nimsiꞌn kywutz tkyaqil xjal noq tuꞌn t-xtalbꞌil qMan Dios ex qAjaw Jesucrist. 
\c 2  
\s1 Aj tyekꞌin te tibꞌjo ichin bꞌinchil ilxix 
\p  
\v 1 Atziꞌn tiꞌjjo tulil qAjaw Jesucrist, ex tiꞌjjo aj qchmet junx tukꞌa,\x + \xo 2:1\xt 1Tes. 4:15-17.\x* qo kubꞌsil qwutza kyeꞌy, erman,  
\v 2 tuꞌn mi jaw kytxꞌixpinjiꞌy kynabꞌla, ex mi chi jaw xobꞌa, qa at juntl xnaqꞌtzbꞌil, nyakutlaj tuꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan, mo tuꞌn jun yol, aj tok kybꞌiꞌn, mo tuꞌn jun uꞌj, nyakutlaj awoꞌy xqox smaꞌnte, ex qa ntqꞌmaꞌn qa lu tqꞌijil qAjaw ma tzul, qa chiꞌ.  
\v 3 Mi txi kyqꞌoꞌn kyibꞌa tuꞌn kykubꞌ sbꞌuꞌn kyuꞌnxjal, quꞌn aj naꞌmxtaq tpon tqꞌijil tuꞌn tul qAjaw, ok chi qꞌojlilxjal tiꞌj qMan Dios nej, ex antza kꞌwele tyekꞌin ichin tibꞌ, a ajqꞌojxix tiꞌj Dios, a o tzꞌel qꞌoꞌn te najin te jun majx.  
\v 4 Quꞌn atzin ichin lo kjawil tnimsin tibꞌ twutz Dios,\x + \xo 2:4\xt Dan. 11:36; Ez. 28:2; Mt. 24:15; Mr. 13:14.\x* ex kqꞌojlil tiꞌj tkyaqil kydiosxjal ex tiꞌj tkyaqil kꞌulbꞌil. Ex okpe kꞌwel qe toj tnejil ja te kynabꞌl nxjalila Dios, ayeꞌ aj Judiy. Ex k-okil tqꞌoꞌn tibꞌ nyakuj Dios. Ex ok tqꞌmaꞌbꞌil: Ayiꞌn weꞌ Dios, chilaꞌ. 
\p  
\v 5 ¿Mitzin naꞌn kyuꞌn, tej t-xi nqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy tiꞌj tkyaqiljo lo, tej intinxtaqa kyukꞌiy?  
\v 6 Ex atzin jaꞌlin, bꞌiꞌn kyuꞌn tiꞌ ma tzꞌok meqonte, tuꞌn mi tzule ichin lo. Naꞌmx tkanin tqꞌijil.  
\v 7 Atziꞌn tipin nya bꞌaꞌn, n-aqꞌnin jaꞌlin twutz txꞌotxꞌ toj ewajil, tzmaxiꞌ aj teljo a meqolte.  
\v 8 Bꞌeꞌxsin kꞌwel tyekꞌiꞌn ichin tibꞌ, a aj ilxix, me bꞌeꞌx kꞌwel bꞌyoꞌn tuꞌn qAjaw, noq tukꞌa T-xew.\x + \xo 2:8\xt Is. 11:4.\x* Ex noq tuꞌn tqoptzꞌajiyil tten, bꞌeꞌx kꞌwel yuchꞌj te jun majx.  
\v 9 Atzin ichin aj ilxix tzul noq tuꞌn tipin satanás, a tajaw il. Ex kꞌwel tbꞌinchin nim techil tipin, a noq tuꞌn kyjaw kaꞌylajkuxjal tiꞌj, me noq te sbꞌuꞌbꞌl.\x + \xo 2:9\xt Mt. 24:24.\x* 
\v 10 Ex kꞌwel tbꞌinchin tkyaqil wiq il, noq tuꞌn kysbꞌetku xjal tuꞌn, aye kyjaꞌ kyxiꞌ toj najin, quꞌn kykyꞌeꞌ tuꞌn kynimin tiꞌjjo Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil, a twutzxix, tuꞌn kyklet.  
\v 11 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, ax Dios kxel tzaqpinkye tuꞌn kykubꞌ sbꞌuꞌn, ex tuꞌn t-xi kynimin a yol nya twutzx,  
\v 12 tuꞌntzin kynaj te jun majx, quꞌn kykyꞌeꞌ tuꞌn t-xi kynimin Tbꞌanil Tqanil, quꞌn noq oꞌkx nchi tzalaj tuꞌn kybꞌinchin il. 
\s1 Ma qo jaw skꞌoꞌn tuꞌn qMan Dios tuꞌn qklet 
\p  
\v 13 Me metzin kyeꞌ, erman, ayiꞌy kꞌuꞌjlinqiꞌy tuꞌn qAjaw, o chi jaw skꞌoꞌn atxix ojtxe tuꞌn qMan Dios, tuꞌn kykleta, noq tuꞌn o saqix kyanmiꞌn tuꞌn Xewbꞌaj Xjan, ex tuꞌn o chi nimiꞌn tiꞌj Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil, a twutzxix. Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, kukx kxel qqꞌoꞌnjiꞌy chjonte te Dios kyiꞌja.  
\v 14 Ikytziꞌn, ma chi txokliꞌy tuꞌn qMan Dios tuꞌn kykleta, noq tuꞌn Tbꞌanil Tqanil kolbꞌil, a xi qqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy, tuꞌntziꞌn jaꞌlin at kyokliꞌn tiꞌjjo a at toj kyaꞌj, jaꞌ nqoptzꞌaje qAjaw Jesucrist. 
\p  
\v 15 Tuꞌnpetziꞌn, ayiꞌy erman, chi weꞌxixa jikyin wen toj kynimbꞌila, ex mi tzꞌel naj toj kykꞌuꞌja a xnaqꞌtzbꞌil xi qqꞌoꞌn kyeꞌy, tej otoꞌxtaqa kyukꞌiy, ex tojjo uꞌj xi qsmaꞌn kyeꞌy.\x + \xo 2:15\xt 1Co. 11:2.\x* 
\v 16-17 Aku qAjaw Jesucrist ex qMan Dios o tzꞌok kꞌuꞌjlinqe, ex o tzaj tqꞌoꞌn jun qꞌuqbꞌil qkꞌuꞌj te jun majx. Ex tuꞌn ikyjo, tzaj tqꞌoꞌn jun tbꞌanil tumil tuꞌn kyayoꞌn tiꞌjjo a at toj kyaꞌj, noq tuꞌn t-xtalbꞌil. Axit qAjaw ex qMan Dios nimsin te kyanmiꞌn ex tuꞌn kyweꞌxixa kujxix, tuꞌntzin kyyoliꞌn ex tuꞌn kybꞌinchintejiꞌy wenxix toj tkyaqil. 
\c 3  
\s1 Qo naꞌn Dios, tuꞌn tkanin Tyol Dios toj tkyaqil twutz txꞌotxꞌ 
\p  
\v 1 Atzin jaꞌlin, erman, chi naꞌn Diosa qiꞌja, tuꞌn tkanin Tbꞌanil Tqanil qAjaw liwey toj tkyaqil twutz txꞌotxꞌ, ex tuꞌn tkubꞌ nimin, tzeꞌnkuxjo tej xpon kanin kyxola.  
\v 2 Ex chi naꞌn Diosa qiꞌja tuꞌn qkleta toj kyqꞌobꞌxjal piꞌsqe ex aj ilqe, quꞌn nya tkyaqilxjal nimilqe tiꞌj Tyol Dios.  
\v 3 Me me te Dios tzꞌaqlexix teꞌ, ex chi kꞌwel tzyuꞌn tuꞌn jikyinxix, ajxi tjapin bꞌaj tkyaqil; ex ok chi elil kloꞌn tuꞌn, toj tqꞌobꞌ tajaw il.  
\v 4 Ex qꞌuqle qe qkꞌuꞌj tiꞌj qAjaw, quꞌn atziꞌn xi qqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy, ax nkubꞌ kybꞌinchinjiꞌy, ex noqit kukx kubꞌ kybꞌinchinjiꞌy.  
\v 5 Axit qAjaw tzꞌonin kyeꞌy, tuꞌn tel kynikyꞌa te tqꞌaqꞌbꞌil tkꞌuꞌj qMan Dios kyukꞌiy, ex tuꞌn kykujsin te kyibꞌa, tzeꞌnku te Crist, toj tkyaqiljo a n-ikyꞌx kyuꞌn. 
\s1 Il tiꞌj tuꞌn qaqꞌnin 
\p  
\v 6 Atzin jaꞌlin erman, kxel qqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy toj tbꞌi qAjaw Jesucrist, tuꞌn tel kypaꞌn kyibꞌa tiꞌj tkyaqiljo erman, a tkyꞌeꞌ tuꞌn taqꞌnin, ex mi nbꞌet tzeꞌnku tojjo xnaqꞌtzbꞌil, a xi qyekꞌiꞌn.  
\v 7 Qalaꞌ bꞌiꞌn kyuꞌn qa il tiꞌj tuꞌn kyok lipeꞌy tiꞌjjo yekꞌbꞌil xkubꞌ qqꞌoꞌn kywutza, quꞌn nyataq kyꞌajqoꞌy kyxola,  
\v 8 ex mix jaꞌ xqo ok waniꞌy kyiꞌja. Qalaꞌ ma qo aqꞌniꞌn qꞌijl ex qnikyꞌin, tuꞌntzin mi tzꞌoke jun iqtz kyiꞌja.\x + \xo 3:8\xt Kybꞌi. 18:3; 1Tes. 2:9.\x* 
\v 9 ¿Quꞌn noqittzin ntiꞌtaq qokliꞌn tiꞌj jun onbꞌil, tuꞌn t-xi qqaniꞌn kyeꞌy? Me mi xi qqaniꞌn. Qalaꞌ ma qo aqꞌniꞌn, tuꞌntzintla tkyij qqꞌoꞌn jun yekꞌbꞌil kyeꞌy, tuꞌn kyok lipeꞌy tiꞌj.  
\v 10 Quꞌn tej qteꞌn kyukꞌiy, xi qnikꞌuꞌn kyeꞌy, qa at jun aꞌla tkyꞌeꞌ tzꞌaqꞌnin, ex ntiꞌ tuꞌn twaꞌn.  
\v 11 Nxi qnaꞌnjiꞌy luꞌn kyeꞌy, quꞌn bꞌiꞌn quꞌn qa at junjun kyxola, a kykyꞌeꞌ chi aqꞌnin, ex noq n-ex kyqꞌij kybꞌetbꞌin kytziyile ja.  
\v 12 Me aye xjal lo kxel qqꞌmaꞌn kye toj tbꞌi qAjaw Jesucrist, tuꞌn kyaqꞌnin, tuꞌntzintla tkanbꞌitjo telix kyqꞌij kyuꞌn.  
\v 13 Ayiꞌy erman, mi chi sikytiꞌy tuꞌn kybꞌinchintejiꞌy wen.\x + \xo 3:13\xt Gal. 6:9.\x* 
\p  
\v 14 Ex qa at jun kyxola mi nkubꞌ tbꞌiꞌn a nxi qqꞌmaꞌn kyeꞌy tojjo uꞌj lo, noq kykaꞌyinka, exsin kypamil kyibꞌa tiꞌj, tuꞌntzin ttzaj txꞌixwe.  
\v 15 Me mi tzꞌel kyikyꞌiꞌn, qalaꞌ kyqꞌoꞌnxa jun tnabꞌl, quꞌn erman. 
\s1 Jun tqꞌolbꞌil Pabl ex jun naꞌj Dios tuꞌn tjapin bꞌajjo uꞌj lo 
\p  
\v 16 Noqit ax qAjaw, a Tajaw tkyaqil nukꞌbꞌil, kukx tzaj qꞌonte tnukꞌbꞌil toj tkyaqil. Ex axit qAjaw ten kyukꞌiy toj tkyaqil.  
\v 17 Atzin qꞌolbꞌil luꞌn ayinkuy Pabl nchin kubꞌ tzꞌibꞌiꞌnte tzeꞌnkuxjo nkubꞌ ntzꞌibꞌinjiꞌy tkyaqil wuꞌja. Ex ikytzin k-elile kynikyꞌjiꞌy te, qa ayinkuy nchin kubꞌ tzꞌibꞌinte uꞌj lo. 
\p  
\v 18 Noqit a t-xtalbꞌil qAjaw Jesucrist kyibꞌaja kykyaqila. Ikyxitjo.